-07T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"因為HA班醫生user唔肯放權 驚俾人搶飯碗，所以寧願谷爆d在行醫生都不肯其他學校開醫療科。"},{"pid":"784d00e92478f0ef5e9af1ea73620fcf11db6139","tid":2233692,"uid":236414,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T14:28:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b99db3ca2499e1253ed011b4e443a9ba7a9761d","tid":2233692,"uid":132462,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"除咗醫生藥劑師<br />\n<br />\npoly 神科grad 都可以砌到間醫院出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57823cd8ac300cba4d967c5408a706bbddc4ae9","tid":2233692,"uid":205378,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:30:03.000Z","msg":"「搏士」？打好啲字先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開醫學院？你估好似開間補習社，搵間班房整吓notes就得咁容易咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要搵醫院教學，又要起科研設施，咁多個專科去邊度搵咁多教授黎教？<br />\n當年中大開都要靠英國啲教授黎幫手，先追得上港大同俾英國/國際間承認<br />\n今時今日香港咁既形勢，邊個仲會肯黎？<br />\n<br />\n除非真係有班本地有heart有經驗既醫生同埋教授出手籌組<br />\n不過公家嗰啲做到死，私家嗰啲又大把錢搵<br />\n應該好難有咁既機會"},{"pid":"e7301474d3323c9df52c140e71972501a363e4d1","tid":2233692,"uid":361247,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"28269e2a37f1829ce0ef53ffc327a28a3ca53d53","tid":2233692,"uid":374441,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"係都科大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T19:01:29.000Z","msg":"其實科大可以買隔離大埔仔村,碧水新村既地比佢起醫學院。<br />\n而且科大係國際排名已經超越港大"},{"pid":"7febcbac3570ce5b215bdad80c47ba447add9c38","tid":2233692,"uid":329324,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"784d00e92478f0ef5e9af1ea73620fcf11db6139","tid":2233692,"uid":236414,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"28269e2a37f1829ce0ef53ffc327a28a3ca53d53","tid":2233692,"uid":374441,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12